    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2026-04-30</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2026-05-07T14:29:26Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution calls on elected officials, faith leaders, and civil society leaders to condemn and counter acts of anti-Semitism.</p><p>The resolution also honors the contributions of Jewish-American&nbsp;servicemembers and&nbsp;commits to ensuring all Americans, including Jewish Americans, can worship without fear of violence or persecution.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
